How to spend the year-end holidays in Singapore
Singapore has plenty to do all year round, but if you’ve picked to visit during this time of year, you’re in for a treat. We’ve got you covered with these picks—from cultural celebrations and music festivals to art exhibitions, sporting events and foodie weekends. Good vibes and festive cheer guaranteed.
